packageManagers.label: Homebrew
packageManagers.installCodeHtml: $ brew tap hashicorp/tap $ brew install hashicorp/tap/nomad-enterprise

packageManagers.label: Ubuntu/Debian
commands: sudo apt update && sudo apt install nomad-enterprise
packageManagers.installCodeHtml: $ wget -O- https://apt.releases.hashicorp.com/gpg | sudo gpg --dearmor -o /usr/share/keyrings/hashicorp-archive-keyring.gpg $ echo "deb [signed-by=/usr/share/keyrings/hashicorp-archive-keyring.gpg] https://apt.releases.hashicorp.com $(lsb_release -cs) main" | sudo tee /etc/apt/sources.list.d/hashicorp.list $ sudo apt update && sudo apt install nomad-enterprise

packageManagers.label: CentOS/RHEL
packageManagers.installCodeHtml: $ sudo yum install -y yum-utils $ sudo yum-config-manager --add-repo https://rpm.releases.hashicorp.com/RHEL/hashicorp.repo $ sudo yum -y install nomad-enterprise

packageManagers.label: Fedora
packageManagers.installCodeHtml: $ sudo dnf install -y dnf-plugins-core $ sudo dnf config-manager --add-repo https://rpm.releases.hashicorp.com/fedora/hashicorp.repo $ sudo dnf -y install nomad-enterprise

packageManagers.label: Amazon Linux
packageManagers.installCodeHtml: $ sudo yum install -y yum-utils $ sudo yum-config-manager --add-repo https://rpm.releases.hashicorp.com/AmazonLinux/hashicorp.repo $ sudo yum -y install nomad-enterprise
